Installation instructions
-------------------------

1.) From the tar file

Step 1: Untar the Distributed...tar.gz file
Step 2: cd .../Distributed    // Go into the untarred directory
Step 3: cd Server
Step 4: gcc -pthread -o Server server.c
Step 5: cd ../Client
Step 6: gcc -pthread -lm -o Client client.c


2.) From the git repository [Read-only access]

Step 1: git clone https://sids-aquarius@github.com/sids-aquarius/Distributed-computing.git   [This will create a clone in the pwd]
Step 2: cd Distributed-computing
From Step 3 - Same as in 1.)

To get the latest changes, use git pull



Run instructions
----------------

=> Server - 

Step 1.) Make sure you are in the Server directory
Step 2.) ./Server

=> Client -

Step 1.) Make sure you are in the Client directory
Step 2.) ./Client [ip address of the server]          // not necessary if on the same machine 
